                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6532" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1031</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10385 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大旱云霓：RT科技的“贸”“疫”成本管理困局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Drought Clouds: The Cost Management Dilemma of RT Technology in &quot;Trade Friction&quot; and &quot; COVID-19&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">程文莉，黎雨鑫，肖梦楠，赵露晞，杨佳莉，余霜，周宁（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆如泰科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链成本管理；目标成本法；中美贸易摩擦；新冠疫情；医疗器械行业；2022百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Value chain cost management; Target costing; Sino-US trade frictions; COVID-19; Medical device industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着全球居民生活水平的提高和医疗卫生意识的增强，医疗器械的市场需求持续增长。然而，当前贸易摩擦与新冠疫情交织的复杂局面却给医疗器械行业带来了诸多挑战，比如不断上涨的原材料成本和海运价格。医械企业要想实现长远稳定发展，就必须加强成本管理。本案例通过描述RT科技在“贸”“疫”背景下面临的成本管理困局，探讨了RT科技应该如何进行成本管理的优化——首先从价值链视角识别RT科技内外部各环节的成本管理问题，然后提出采用目标成本法作为价值链成本管理工具的思路，最后思考RT科技应该怎样运用目标成本法应对成本危机。通过本案例的讨论与学习，学生可以掌握价值链成本管理、目标成本法的相关知识与方法，拓展思考“贸”“疫”背景下医疗器械企业的成本管理问题及应对措施。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the improvement of the global population&#39;s living standard and the increase of medical and health awareness, the market demand for medical devices continues to grow. However, the current complex situation of intertwined trade frictions and new crown epidemics has brought many challenges to the medical device industry, such as rising raw material costs and shipping prices. Medical device companies must strengthen cost management if they want to achieve long-term stable development. This case describes the cost management dilemma faced by RT Technology in the context of &quot;trade&quot; and &quot;epidemic&quot;, and discusses how RT Technology should optimize its cost management - firstly, from Then, it proposes the idea of using target cost method as a value chain cost management tool, and finally considers how RT Technology should apply the target cost method to deal with the cost crisis. Through the discussion and study of this case, students can master the knowledge and methods of value chain cost management and target cost method, and expand their thinking about the cost management problems and countermeasures of medical device enterprises in the context of &quot;trade friction&quot; and &quot;COVID-19&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》、《成本管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链理论；价值链成本管理；企业内部价值链(基本活动、辅助活动)；价值链组织间关系管理；价值链组织间交易成本；价值链成本管理工具；目标成本法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
